In Brief
Integration of a large sample size of
glioma tumors with multidimensional
‘omic characterization and clinical
annotation provides insights into
molecular classification, telomere
maintenance mechanisms, progression
from low to high grade disease, driver
mutations, and therapeutic options.
Ceccarelli et al., 2016, Cell 164, 550–563
January 28, 2016 ª2016 Elsevier Inc.
