(F) DNA methylation heatmap of TCGA glioma samples ordered per Figure 2A and the epigenetically regulated (EReg) gene signatures defined for G-CIMP-low,
G-CIMP-high, and Codel subtypes. The mean RNA sequencing counts for each gene matched to the promoter of the identified cgID across each cluster are
plotted to the right.
